ary signals. We highlight previously\nundetected planetary candidates, including several small potential planets in\nthe habitable zone of their host stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Jan 2015 06:34:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 13 Feb 2015 21:19:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-26"}
