uration. The narrow parallel\nmomentum distribution of the core fragment and the strong forward peaking of\nthe valence neutron angular distribution suggest a one-neutron halo\nconfiguration in either of the $2p_{3/2}$ and $2s_{1/2}$ configurations of the\n$^{37}$Mg ground state.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Jan 2015 12:10:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 Mar 2015 10:32:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-04"}
